title: Create New Playlist (Step 1)
custom_preconds: GIVEN a Cerebro event is running
custom_steps: WHEN an Cerebro Operator clicks on End Stream (STREAM_DONE)
custom_expected:
THEN Saberstaff, based on environment, will

PROD
call Cerebro API to calculate in/out points
copy old playlist files to archive folder - mlb-entmedia-saberstaff-prod
overwrite playlist files based on chunks to keep/remove - the original Cerebro directory
update duration in Forge and publish video entity
publish message for Job #2 to pick up

NPD
call Cerebro API to calculate in/out points
copy old playlist files to archive folder - mlb-entmedia-saberstaff-qa
create replica of Cerebro's output (b/c NPD points to a PROD bucket) & overwrite playlist files based on chunks to keep/remove - mlb-entmedia-saberstaff-qa-working
update duration in Forge and publish video entity
publish message for Job #2 to pick up

title: Step 1 - copy old playlist files to archive folder
custom_preconds: GIVEN a Cerebro event is running
custom_steps:
WHEN an Cerebro Operator clicks on End Stream (STREAM_DONE)
AND Step 1 completes successfully
AND you check the archive folder folder

PROD - mlb-entmedia-saberstaff-prod
NPD - mlb-entmedia-saberstaff-qa
custom_expected:
THEN the user will see a full copy of the master playlist and media playlist

![](index.php?/attachments/get/13310524)

title: Step 1 - overwrite playlist files based on chunks to keep/remove
custom_preconds: GIVEN a Cerebro event is running
custom_steps:
WHEN an Cerebro Operator clicks on End Stream (STREAM_DONE)
AND Step 1 completes successfully
AND you check the archive folder folder

PROD - HLS Cloud Bucket on the Event Detail page (i.e. mlb-entmedia-mlb-adhoc-abr-us-mr-prod)
NPD - mlb-entmedia-saberstaff-qa-working
custom_expected:
THEN the user will see
full copy of the master playlist
trimmed media playlist (with ts paths trimmed out)
all ts chunks still present

![](index.php?/attachments/get/13310525)

title: Archive Slate Chunks (Step 2)
custom_preconds:

custom_steps: THEN at schedule time (2am), Saberstaff will
custom_expected:

Pick up messages from Job #1
Move chunks to archive folder - mlb-entmedia-saberstaff-qa

PROD
Pick up messages from Job #1 
Move chunks to archive folder - mlb-entmedia-saberstaff-prod

title: Event Type - Ad Hoc (FLive)
custom_preconds: GIVEN a Cerebro Operator creates a Cerebro event
custom_steps: IF the Event Type is Ad Hoc (Video On Demand Playlist)
custom_expected: THEN Saberstaff will run when the stream is ended

title: Event Type - SLive (SLive)
custom_preconds: GIVEN a Cerebro Operator creates a Cerebro event
custom_steps: IF the Event Type is SLive (Live Playlist - Sliding Window)
custom_expected:
THEN Saberstaff will not run when the stream is ended

The Saberstaff logs will show INFO com.mlb.entmedia.saberstaff.functions.PlaylistTrimFunction - Event 2695 type SLive is not currently supported

title: Event Type - SLive Big Inning (SLive)
custom_preconds: GIVEN a Cerebro Operator creates a Cerebro event
custom_steps: IF the Event Type is SLive Big Inning (Live Playlist - Sliding Window)
custom_expected:

The Saberstaff logs will show INFO com.mlb.entmedia.saberstaff.functions.PlaylistTrimFunction - Event 2698 type SLive - Big Inning is not currently supported

title: Slack Notification - Discontinuity in playlist
custom_preconds:
GIVEN a Cerebro Operator has stopped an Ad Hoc VOD Stream
AND the playlist has discontinuity tag
